description:
The idea of constructing a whole cryptocurrency ecosystem did not emerge out of the blue but was a logical conclusion from a broad experience gained during the development of cryptocurrency projects as well as trading services.
The ecosystem offers a complex of 15 original solutions for:
* Increasing the efficiency of trading activity
* Studying of specificies of crypto trading
* Decreasing the level of risk in the investment field
* Saving time
* Improving trading and investment strategies of users
* Receiving the recent trends in the field
* Closed beta-testing of all developed modules
name: FTEC
